  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/b8f1ad3f3643822748b846b45830832e.avif?t=1751015168\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras_big/b8f1ad3f3643822748b846b45830832e.avif?t=1751015168 width=800 height=598 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Waiting in the Lime forest — It begins with the tragedy of an innocent child's death. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must unravel the mystery alongside those who deserve to fall into hell, in order to uncover the truth. In this point-and-click cinematic suspense game, you will encounter bodies full of secrets and heretical taboos. You might be a sane human being, but to survive in this world, you must confront every dark aspect. The time has come to find the culprit and witness the truth with your own eyes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/2150abaf3061ae61c362c3907db7910c.poster.avif?t=1751015168\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/2150abaf3061ae61c362c3907db7910c.webm?t=1751015168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/2150abaf3061ae61c362c3907db7910c.mp4?t=1751015168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Game System</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Point-and-click</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/55c7ebd419a64d5c342ff47558933f9a.poster.avif?t=1751015168\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/55c7ebd419a64d5c342ff47558933f9a.webm?t=1751015168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/55c7ebd419a64d5c342ff47558933f9a.mp4?t=1751015168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■This Game Includes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-drawn visuals</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel-art style graphics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel font text </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suspense elements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/3070862ac5b5eb15d730152d79c540b0.avif?t=1751015168\" width=132 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Character Introduction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/baac5ac45d7ca565eb770b52adab095a.avif?t=1751015168\" width=250 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Oliver: </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A troubled young man haunted by painful memories and former loves, who becomes lost between reality and fantasy. A charming yet fragile boy in need of support, he stands accused of murder. <br>You must help him rise from the depths!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/40e8f4e6b53ff093fc167dc06ce68553.avif?t=1751015168\" width=250 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Edward: </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The player character.<br>Living a stable life with his wife and dog. <br>A person who lives by the motto of standing by their neighbors and rarely succumbs to emotional strain.<br>With his steady and somewhat oblivious disposition, he accompanies others fearlessly into danger.<br>He is frequently stabbed and occasionally makes his wife cry.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/94961763984719f4ca51703329c94169.avif?t=1751015168\" width=337 height=271 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Max the Golden Retriever: </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your loyal dog. <br>While the character has no significant impact on the plot, Max adds a touch of warmth, embodying the heart of a point-and-click adventure.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/41d395d030aa17d4f6a3e53626956047.poster.avif?t=1751015168\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/41d395d030aa17d4f6a3e53626956047.webm?t=1751015168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/41d395d030aa17d4f6a3e53626956047.mp4?t=1751015168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/b8f1ad3f3643822748b846b45830832e.avif?t=1751015168\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras_big/b8f1ad3f3643822748b846b45830832e.avif?t=1751015168 width=800 height=598 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Waiting in the Lime forest — It begins with the tragedy of an innocent child's death. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must unravel the mystery alongside those who deserve to fall into hell, in order to uncover the truth. In this point-and-click cinematic suspense game, you will encounter bodies full of secrets and heretical taboos. You might be a sane human being, but to survive in this world, you must confront every dark aspect. The time has come to find the culprit and witness the truth with your own eyes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/2150abaf3061ae61c362c3907db7910c.poster.avif?t=1751015168\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/2150abaf3061ae61c362c3907db7910c.webm?t=1751015168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/2150abaf3061ae61c362c3907db7910c.mp4?t=1751015168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Game System</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Point-and-click</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/55c7ebd419a64d5c342ff47558933f