cumbs to emotional strain.<br>With his steady and somewhat oblivious disposition, he accompanies others fearlessly into danger.<br>He is frequently stabbed and occasionally makes his wife cry.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/94961763984719f4ca51703329c94169.avif?t=1751015168\" width=337 height=271 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Max the Golden Retriever: </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your loyal dog. <br>While the character has no significant impact on the plot, Max adds a touch of warmth, embodying the heart of a point-and-click adventure.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/41d395d030aa17d4f6a3e53626956047.poster.avif?t=1751015168\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/41d395d030aa17d4f6a3e53626956047.webm?t=1751015168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/extras/41d395d030aa17d4f6a3e53626956047.mp4?t=1751015168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
